{{Databox|en=Ghomara language}}'''Taɣumarit''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⴰⵖⵓⵎⴰⵕⵜ''') tga yat n tantala n [[Tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas|Tmaziɣt n Waṭlas]], nttat a s ar sawaln [[iɣumariyn]] ɣ ugafa n [[Lmɣrib]] (ɣ Accawen d Tiṭṭawin). Tutlayt ad taẓ bahra i [[Taznagt n Srayr]] d tutlayin n wa[[Tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas|ṭl]]<nowiki/>as yaḍn, mac taggug bahra f [[Tarifit|Trifit]].

Tqriban kran 10,000 n middn ad si-s isawaln.

