== Amawal ==

=== Amdya n tguriwin ===
Amdya n iwaliwn n kraygat ass s Taɣumarit:

* ''targat'': “tawargit”
* ''ahlan'': “azul”
* ''lmakla'': “tirmt”
* ''tanebdut'': “anbdu”

